Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept this from the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.34,00:02:53.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（シカク）火影様よりの書状\N受け取るがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver it to Lord Tsuchikage
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.34,00:03:01.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,土影様に届けよ\N至急　ご返答願いたいとな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and relay to him that we desire\Nan immediate response!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to deliver\Nanything to him.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:01.92,00:03:05.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,届けるまでもない\Nここで返答してやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you your answer\Nright here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's best not\Nto be so hasty.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:18.50,00:03:21.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,慌てぬほうがよいときもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.30,00:03:29.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fourth Kazekage?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.30,00:03:32.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目風影！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Hidden Sand here?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.29,00:03:34.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ　砂隠れが。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hidden Sand territory.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:38.45,00:03:41.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここは　我ら砂隠れの\N国境でもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be unwise to have\Nan incident occur here.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:41.92,00:03:45.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここで騒ぎを起こされては困る。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put out any sparks\Nthat rain down over us.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.15,00:03:49.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,降りかかる火の粉は\N振り払わねばなるまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sand will move accordingly,\Nas the Sand.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:52.07,00:03:54.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,砂は砂として動く。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that,\Nwhatever you decide to do.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:54.47,00:03:57.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それを承知で\N行動してもらいたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:01.27,00:04:03.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,散！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the request to enter into\Nthe peace treaty?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.27,00:04:12.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,平和条約締結の申し込み\Nどうなさるおつもりです？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, it will be turned down.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:12.77,00:04:15.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,当然　お断りなさるんでしょうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the Hidden Leaf negotiates\Nwith the Hidden Sand,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:15.82,00:04:18.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いかに木ノ葉隠れが\N砂隠れと組もうが→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing will challenge\Nthe unity of the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:18.89,00:04:22.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,我らの　一枚岩の結束に\N敵うものはありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,– Right!\N– Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.97,00:04:25.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのとおりです。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.08,00:04:28.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（オオノキ）静まれぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I am proud of\Nthe unity of the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.20,00:04:32.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もちろん　岩隠れの結束は\Nわしの誇りじゃぜ。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:32.90,00:04:37.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし　岩隠れの命運をかけ→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With the pride on our line,\Nwe sent 1000 of our shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:37.03,00:04:40.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,一千余名の忍を投入した\N侵攻作戦を→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear that it took just one of them,\Nthe Yellow Flash, to stop the invasion.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.42,00:04:42.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,頓挫させたのは→
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.45,00:04:46.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,黄色い閃光\Nただ１人だったと聞く。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reality of it.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:46.89,00:04:50.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それもまた事実じゃぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear they're going to enter\Ninto a peace treaty
Dialogue: 0,00:04:58.70,00:05:03.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ライドウ）今度　岩隠れと平和条約が\N締結されるんだってさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Hidden Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How much faith can we put\Nin a single piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:03.07,00:05:06.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ゲンマ）紙切れ一枚に\Nどんだけ効力があるか。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:06.54,00:05:09.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ガイ）うむ…　それは言える。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, think about\Nthe burden on Lord Third!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.20,00:05:12.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前たちも\N三代目様の苦労も考えろって。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the long, great war\Nwill be over for now.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.82,00:05:16.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（アスマ）とにかく長かった大戦も\Nひとまず　これで終わりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's toast with some dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.90,00:05:18.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（紅）おだんごで乾杯しましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:23.52,00:05:26.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ガイ）お～い　カカシ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to join us for some dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.32,00:05:28.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こっち来て　だんご食わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not too sociable these days.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.12,00:05:46.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最近　つきあい悪いな　アイツ。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:46.84,00:05:49.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,悩みでもあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something bothering him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't expect him\Nto be jumping for joy.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:49.69,00:05:53.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そりゃ　手放しで　はしゃげる\N心境じゃないだろ。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:53.84,00:05:58.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　オビトとリンのことが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about\NObito and Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.64,00:06:02.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ　心に大きな傷が残るさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That would definitely leave\Na hole in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.47,00:06:13.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((カカシ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.80,00:06:16.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,リン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,HOW A SHINOBI SHOULD DIE
Dialogue: 0,00:06:44.44,00:06:46.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ホムラ）ご苦労じゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can breathe\Na sigh of relief for a while.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.40,00:06:48.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（コハル）ひとまず胸を\Nなでおろしたわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied with\Nan agreement like this?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.92,00:06:51.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ダンゾウ）こんな条約で満足ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To forgive\Nthe Hidden Stone's actions
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.55,00:06:53.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,岩隠れの活動を認め→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and drop our demands\Nfor compensation...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:53.74,00:06:57.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,賠償請求権を放棄するとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though we lost the war!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.17,00:07:00.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,戦争に負けたも同然の内容。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:02.42,00:07:04.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヒルゼンは　どう思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hiruzen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuing the war\Nany further would be disastrous
Dialogue: 0,00:07:04.90,00:07:07.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ヒルゼン）これ以上の戦争の継続は→
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.55,00:07:10.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,疲弊しきった木ノ葉にとっても\N致命的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for the already\Nexhausted Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a step toward finding\Ncommon ground...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.97,00:07:14.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,同意を導き出すための譲歩…。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.08,00:07:16.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,このたびの大戦で→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of my friends gave\Ntheir lives for this great war!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:16.20,00:07:18.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,多くの盟友たちが\N犠牲になっておる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they died in vain!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.93,00:07:22.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,彼らを犬死にさせたも同然だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I assume full responsibility\Nfor that.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:25.74,00:07:29.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その責任は\Nすべて火影である　わしにある。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:29.40,00:07:33.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どう責任をとるつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,00:07:33.77,00:07:37.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目火影の座を辞し→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to step down as the Third Hokage,\Nand have the Fourth Hokage installed.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:37.08,00:07:40.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目に譲るつもりじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:46.35,00:07:49.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,残念だのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How regrettable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage was\Ndoing a fine job...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:49.75,00:07:54.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目は　よくやっておったが。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:54.35,00:07:59.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,元を正せば\N三代目が甘い考えゆえ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth be told, the Third Hokage\Nwas too soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and he allowed the village\Nto be pushed into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:59.49,00:08:02.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あそこまで\N里が追い込まれたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.69,00:08:07.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今　必要とされる火影とは\N里に変革を成し→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a Hokage\Nwho will change things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and enforce the laws of the shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:07.32,00:08:11.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍に掟を徹底させる。\Nそんな人材だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We need someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Is there such a person?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:11.39,00:08:14.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ほう　適当な者はおるのかえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend Orochimaru,\None of the Legendary Sannin.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:17.13,00:08:20.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは　伝説の三忍と謳われる→
Dialogue: 0,00:08:20.17,00:08:23.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸を推薦する。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,– Oh...\N– Him?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:23.98,00:08:26.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目は　どう思うのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Lord Third?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:26.95,00:08:32.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸は\N戦乱の時代にあってこそ→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru is truly a genius\Nin this age of war.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:32.17,00:08:37.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,才能に満ち溢れる天才\Nと言えましょう。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.55,00:08:42.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし　その瞳の奥には→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A sinister will and greed lurk\Ndeep behind those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:42.00,00:08:44.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,悪意と野望が潜んでおります。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:44.85,00:08:47.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのような素養を持つ者に→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a person cannot be given\Nthe duties of a Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:47.49,00:08:49.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影は任せられませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Third!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:49.49,00:08:52.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目！
Dialogue: 0,00:08:52.47,00:08:56.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,波風ミナトを推薦いたします。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend Minato Namikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A pupil of Jiraiya...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:56.03,00:08:58.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也の弟子筋にあたる男。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Na disciple of your disciple.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:58.75,00:09:01.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,つまり　三代目の孫弟子じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A man so skilled,\Nhe's nicknamed the Yellow Flash.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.44,00:09:04.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,黄色い閃光と異名をとる手練。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:04.35,00:09:06.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ほう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato is still too young.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:08.29,00:09:12.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ミナトは　まだ若い！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:12.69,00:09:15.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,神無毘橋に勝利し→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He emerged victorious\Nat the Battle of Kannabi Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:15.08,00:09:19.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,第三次忍界大戦\N終結に導いた功績は大。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and distinguished himself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,by leading the way to end\Nof the Third Great Shinobi War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am opposed!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:19.82,00:09:21.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは反対だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:27.42,00:09:30.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,他の皆は　どうじゃえ？
Dialogue: 0,00:09:54.92,00:09:58.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は　火の意志を\N継ぐ者と思っておる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you will carry on\Nthe Will of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to entrust you with\Nthe future of the Hidden Leaf...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.87,00:10:05.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなお前に　これからの木ノ葉を\Nそして　忍世界の未来を託す。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the shinobi world.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:05.57,00:10:08.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,受けてくれるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You will accept, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:08.35,00:10:12.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ミナト）三代目の信頼に\Nお応えできるように。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall do my best to deserve\Nyour trust, Lord Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have passed this on\Nunder better circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:12.75,00:10:16.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,本来なら　もっと\Nよい環境を整えたうえで→
Dialogue: 0,00:10:16.72,00:10:20.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,引き継げたらと\N思っていたのだが→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What lies ahead is not peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:20.20,00:10:24.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,目の前に広がるのは\N平穏な未来ではない。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:24.72,00:10:27.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,覚悟はできています。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.25,00:10:30.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うむ。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:30.20,00:10:33.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前なら　やってくれるじゃろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:52.92,00:10:55.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなとこで　どうしたってばね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.80,00:10:58.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目様からのお呼び出しは→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Lord Third want with you?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:58.02,00:11:00.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何だったの？\Nああ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get scolded?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:00.47,00:11:02.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か　お小言をもらったのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?\NDon't worry about it, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.50,00:11:04.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,平気　平気！　そんなの→
Dialogue: 0,00:11:04.52,00:11:06.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,気にすることないってばね！
Dialogue: 0,00:11:06.47,00:11:09.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや　そうじゃなくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:09.19,00:11:11.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　何だってばね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.55,00:11:15.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの…　四代目の火影をやれと。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to be\Nthe Fourth Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.50,00:11:17.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうだってばね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?\NDon't mind the Hokage—
Dialogue: 0,00:11:17.45,00:11:21.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影なんか　気にすることない…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.80,00:11:24.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今　何て言ったってばね！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been named the Fourth Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:26.47,00:11:29.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目火影を仰せつかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:32.49,00:11:34.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おめでとうだってばね！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.49,00:11:36.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おいおい！
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.13,00:11:42.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お役目　ご苦労さまです！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for\Nall your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.78,00:11:44.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:56.47,00:12:00.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヒルゼンの思惑どおりの\N流れになってしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all going Hiruzen's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage intends to\Nuse Minato as a puppet
Dialogue: 0,00:12:00.42,00:12:04.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（大蛇丸）三代目の本心は\Nミナトを傀儡とし→
Dialogue: 0,00:12:04.08,00:12:07.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,師弟で木ノ葉を牛耳ることね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep ruling the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Hidden Leaf\Nhas no future.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:07.12,00:12:10.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,このままのやり方では\N木ノ葉に未来はない。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:10.73,00:12:13.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まだ諦めることはありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:13.93,00:12:15.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この研究が成功すれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If my research is successful,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:15.92,00:12:20.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉隠れの権力を\N掌握するなど　たやすいこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be easy to grasp\Nthe power of the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.90,00:12:22.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To grasp power...\Nstronger measures must be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.95,00:12:28.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,権力を握るためなら\N多少　強引な手段を使う用意も。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\Nwe won't be choosing measures.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.39,00:12:31.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,時が来れば手段は選ばぬ。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.30,00:12:34.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし　今はまだ　その時ではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's not time yet.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:39.39,00:12:44.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だいたい　あやつに人望があれば\Nもう少し　なんとか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, if he's popular at all,\Nhe should...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.90,00:12:48.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　甲！　乙！　丙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kinoe, Kinoto, Hinoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,– Sir!\N– Sir!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:48.40,00:12:51.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（３人）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:13:00.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,I, HIRUZEN SARUTOBI, HEREBY ANNOUNCE\NMY RESIGNATION AS HOKAGE, AND APPOINT\NMINATO NAMIKAZE AS THE FOURTH HOKAGE.\NSIGNED, THIRD HOKAGE HIRUZEN SARUTOBI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.58,00:13:03.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,な…　なんと！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:08.77,00:13:12.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ガイ）お～い　カカシ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.70,00:13:17.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,「いかに死すべきか」！？\Nなんだ　これ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"How a Shinobi Should Die"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:17.72,00:13:19.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,返してくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.80,00:13:22.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何ごとだ？\Nあっ　そうだった！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fourth Hokage\Nwas just announced!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:22.34,00:13:26.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今　四代目火影が発表された！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shocked!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:26.70,00:13:29.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,びっくりすんなよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato Sensei will be\Nthe Fourth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:29.08,00:13:32.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目火影は　ミナト先生だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,RIN NOHARA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.85,00:13:42.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,リン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like Minato Sensei\Nis going to be Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:42.83,00:13:47.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ミナト先生が火影になるそうだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato Sensei will be\Nthe Professor's successor
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.92,00:13:51.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先生なら\Nプロフェッサーの後継者となり→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and change the Hidden Leaf...\Nand the shinobi world.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:51.17,00:13:53.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉隠れの里を…。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:53.52,00:13:56.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍の世界を変えてくれる。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.95,00:14:02.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう　お前たちのような\N犠牲を出すことは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any more sacrifices\Nlike you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you...\NFourth Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:27.62,00:14:31.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,頼むぞ　四代目。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:31.00,00:14:34.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,一命にかえても。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall dedicate my life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi. You shouldn't use {\i0}\N{\i1}that jutsu anymore. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:04.14,00:15:09.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((カカシ　さっきのあの術は\Nもう使わないほうがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From what I could see,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:09.18,00:15:12.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,見たところ　一点集中型の突き。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your focused concentrated attack{\i0}\N{\i1}undoubtedly has power and speed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:12.81,00:15:15.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,確かに破壊力とスピードはあるけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it makes you move too fast {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:15.16,00:15:17.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自分自身の移動スピードが速すぎて→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be able to ascertain {\i0}\N{\i1}your opponent's counterattack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:17.99,00:15:20.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,相手のカウンターを\N見切ることができない→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's still an imperfect jutsu. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:20.63,00:15:25.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(不完全な術だからね))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those were Minato Sensei's words{\i0}\N{\i1}back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.21,00:15:30.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あのとき　ミナト先生は\Nああおっしゃったが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obito...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.76,00:15:34.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《オビト…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm giving you... my Sharingan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.18,00:15:43.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((オビト：この　俺の写輪眼を\Nやるからよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever the village may say...{\i0}\N{\i1}you are... a great jonin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.83,00:15:53.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里のヤツらが何て言おうと\Nお前は立派な上忍だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I really feel...{\i0}\N{\i1}So please accept it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:53.11,00:15:57.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それが　俺の気持だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.46,00:16:00.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(受け取ってくれ))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gave me this Sharingan{\i0}\N{\i1}in my left eye...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:00.63,00:16:05.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《お前にもらった\Nこの左目の写輪眼。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Chidori and Sharingan became one, {\i0}\N{\i1}it became a complete jutsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.59,00:16:11.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,千鳥と写輪眼が一つになったとき\Nこの術は完全になった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... that jutsu took Rin's life. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:11.16,00:16:14.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし　その術でリンの命を…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:16.78,00:16:18.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,千鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you've been!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:30.59,00:16:32.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんなところにいたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a mission.\NYou've been summoned immediately.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:32.59,00:16:36.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,任務だから　すぐ出頭しろって。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:45.58,00:16:48.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.07,00:16:52.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,任務ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I want you to retrieve the documents\Nrelating to the peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.21,00:16:57.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ。　平和条約に関する書類を\N受け取ってきてもらいたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:57.41,00:16:59.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still some shinobi\Nwho desire war.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.36,00:17:04.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍の中には\Nまだ戦乱の世を望む勢力もいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are rumors that they are trying\Nto steal the documents to create discord.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:04.19,00:17:06.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その者たちが書類を奪い→
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.23,00:17:10.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仲違いさせようとしている\Nという情報がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.12,00:17:12.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心して任務にかかってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:12.54,00:17:14.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll wrap this up! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:29.53,00:17:33.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《一気に　かたをつける！　千鳥》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:33.69,00:17:35.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((リン：カカシ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:35.82,00:17:41.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ　カカシ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:41.28,00:17:43.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カカシ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:54.68,00:17:57.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Severe Leaf Hurricanes!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:57.21,00:17:59.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ガイ）木ノ葉　剛力旋風！
Dialogue: 0,00:18:02.84,00:18:04.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クッ！　新手か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:04.79,00:18:09.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前らしくもない！\N何をぼやっとしている！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you!\NWhy are you spaced out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:09.79,00:18:13.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,す　すまん…。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:13.64,00:18:15.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:22.34,00:18:24.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しっかりしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:30.53,00:18:33.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか…。\Nはい。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Kakashi like that.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:36.46,00:18:39.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あんなカカシは\N見たことがありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I secretly sent you.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:39.81,00:18:42.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,密かに同行してもらって\Nよかったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To help him at a time like this...\NThat's what an eternal rival is for!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:42.81,00:18:45.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんなときこそ\N永遠のライバルとしては→
Dialogue: 0,00:18:45.92,00:18:49.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何かしてやらないと！\Nとは思うのですが！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already done a lot.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:49.64,00:18:52.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう十分やってくれた。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:52.11,00:18:55.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あとは任せてもらえるかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you leave the rest to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,HIDDEN LEAF HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.48,00:19:13.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato Sensei! I mean... Lord Fourth...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.07,00:19:19.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ミナト先生！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:19.09,00:19:21.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや　四代目！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:21.61,00:19:25.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今までどおりの呼び名でいいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Address me as you always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some in the village think I'm not qualified\Nfor the position and oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:27.43,00:19:30.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だいたい\N俺がふさわしい人材なのか→
Dialogue: 0,00:19:30.56,00:19:33.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里の中でも\N反対の立場の者もいるしね。
Dialogue: 0,00:19:36.24,00:19:38.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今日　ここに来たのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here today...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:38.66,00:19:43.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,キミに　火影直属の\N暗部への配属を命じるためだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to assign you to the ANBU\Nunder my direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:47.31,00:19:49.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ俺なんかを…。
Dialogue: 0,00:19:49.54,00:19:53.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,右腕となって働いてもらいたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be my right-hand man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,AN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,HOW A SHINOBI SHOULD DIE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,EQUIPMENT DEPT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a set of gear for you.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:26.23,00:20:28.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あなたの装備一式です。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:32.84,00:20:34.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます。
